  "texts": [
    "The exclusion criteria were as follows: (1) questions that violate ethical or legal standards; (2) questions with obvious biases or conflicts of interest; and (3) questions involving complex conditions and multiple severe organ diseases.",
    "In the direct GPT-4 group, users input questions directly into the GPT-4.",
    "The system automatically recorded both the questions and final answers.",
    "The System Prompt (\"Please act as a nurse specialist in breast cancer to assist me.\")",
    "for GPT-4 was consistent with that for the RAG-GPT group."
  ]
